				#parent : @7,
				#content : 'I am NeoJSONObjectMapping.\rI describe how instances of a Smalltalk class are mapped to a JSON map.\r\rI do this using set of NeoJSONPropertyMappings.\r\rI know the Smalltalk class that I am a mapping for. This class is the schema identifier and is used to instanciate new objects.\r\rA mapping can be based on any combination of instance variables or accessors (getter/setter pairs). \r\rI offer a builder interface to constuct property mappings.',
