					#isMeta : false
				},
				#parent : @7,
				#content : 'I am NeoJSONMappingNotFound. I am signalled when no mapping is found for a schema.\r\rPortability comment: In Pharo,  I could technically subclass from NotFound directly, avoid all my defined methods and only keep #messageText and #standardMessageText. However, NotFound exception does not exist in other dialects. To keep NeoJSON as portable as possible we duplicate some Pharo code into myself. ',
