			#sourceCode : 'upToEnd\r\t"Parse and collect JSON values from my stream until it ends, returning the collection.\r\tThis supports Newline delimited JSON (application/x-ndjson) & JSON Lines (application/jsonl).\r\tWarning: though each element is valid JSON, taken as a whole the result is non-valid JSON."\r\t\r\t^ Array streamContents: [ :out |\r\t\t[ self atEnd ] whileFalse: [ out nextPut: self next ] ]',
