			},
			#name : #'atPath:',
			#protocol : #accessing,
			#sourceCode : 'atPath: keyCollection\r\t"Use each key in keyCollection recursively, return nil when a key is missing.\r\tNote how keys can also be indexes to arrays."\r\r\t| value |\r\tvalue := self.\r\tkeyCollection do: [ :each |\r\t\tvalue := value at: each ifAbsent: [ ^ nil ] ].\r\t^ value',
