				#isMeta : false
			},
			#name : #'atPath:add:',
			#protocol : #adding,
			#sourceCode : 'atPath: keyCollection add: newValue\r\t"Use each key in keyCollection recursively, create new levels when needed.\r\tNote how keys can also be indexes to arrays.\r\tThis variant will insert/add to arrays"\r\r\t| target |\r\tkeyCollection ifEmpty: [ ^ self ].\r\ttarget := self.\r\tkeyCollection allButLastDo: [ :each |\r\t\ttarget := target \r\t\t\tat: each\r\t\t\tifAbsent: [ target at: each add: target species new ] ].\r\t^ target at: keyCollection last add: newValue',
			#stamp : '',
			#package : #Neo-JSON-Core
		}
