			#sourceCode : 'atPath: keyCollection put: newValue\r\t"Use each key in keyCollection recursively, create new levels when needed.\r\tNote how keys can also be indexes to arrays."\r\r\t| target |\r\tkeyCollection ifEmpty: [ ^ self ].\r\ttarget := self.\r\tkeyCollection allButLastDo: [ :each |\r\t\ttarget := target \r\t\t\tat: each\r\t\t\tifAbsent: [ target at: each put: target species new ] ].\r\t^ target at: keyCollection last put: newValue',
