			},
			#name : #'at:ifPresent:ifAbsentPut:',
			#protocol : #accessing,
			#sourceCode : 'at: key ifPresent: aPresentBlock ifAbsentPut: anAbsentBlock\r\t"Lookup the given key in the receiver. If it is present, answer the\r\tvalue of evaluating the first block optionally with the value associated with the key.\r\tOtherwise store and return the result of evaluating the second block as the new value of the key."\r\r\t"Overwritten to patch a bug in the superclass implementation in Pharo 7 and 8.\r\tThis problem was fixed in Pharo 9 where this overwrite is no longer necessary but harmless."\r\r\t^ self\r\t\tat: key\r\t\tifPresent: aPresentBlock\r\t\tifAbsent: [ self at: key put: anAbsentBlock value ]',
			#stamp : '',
			#package : #Neo-JSON-Core
		}
	}
}OmEntry {
